Products.Description:
Cocoa Brown 1 Hour Tan Dark needs just one application and is perfect for:
Olive skinned ladies who like a deep, dark tan.
Medium toned ladies who want to experiment with a more bronzed glow.
Paler ladies who often need multiple layers of tan to get any colour at all!
This is the darker version of our original Cocoa Brown 1 Hour Tan. It's the same great formula-just darker!
Accelerating ingredients mean that this revolutionary, speedy self tan develops into a Dark cocoa brown colour in just 1 Hour.
Vegetable derived tanning agent & preservative - gentle on sensitive skin - No Parabens.
Note: Tan continues to develop after rinsing.
